              Episode Notes:

         
          In Kansas City, MO a young man is found dead in the middle of 
          an apartment complex. With no leads or witnesses, Detective Ed 
          Begley is hoping the victim&#039;s cell phone can help him find the 
          killer. In Memphis, a case gets personal for Sgt. Caroline Mason
